Package icarus.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AlreadyAtStateException
    Thrown when a component's state is changed to a state it is already at
    ComponentFailedException
    Thrown when a command is given to a failed component
    FixAlreadyUnderwayException
    Thrown when a fix command is issued to a component which is already going through a fix
    InvalidComponentException
    Thrown when an incorrect component is passed to a method
    InvalidPumpException
    Thrown when a call to an invalid pump is issued
    InvalidRodsException
    Thrown when a value outside the allowed boundaries is passed to the reactor
    InvalidValveException
    Thrown when a call to an invalid pump ID is issued
    MaximumRodsException
    Thrown when the control rods of the reactor are raised above their maximum value
    MinimumRodsException
    Thrown when the control rods of the reactor are lowered below their minimum value
    NoFixNeededException
    Thrown when a fix command is issued to functional component
